<section class="w-full py-0">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="border-2 border-slate-300 bg-white">
      <div class="border-b-2 border-slate-300 bg-slate-100 p-4">
        <h2 class="text-[1.4rem] uppercase tracking-wider text-black">
          About the National Federation of Insurance Agents
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="grid gap-4">
            <p class="leading-7 text-slate-900">
              Established as the definitive authority for insurance agent verification, the NFIA operates under federation
              oversight to maintain the highest standards of professional integrity within the insurance industry. Our
              comprehensive certification process ensures that only agents who demonstrate exceptional competency,
              ethical conduct, and professional commitment receive our official verification.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-7 text-slate-900">
