                verification, and unwavering commitment to consumer protection and trust."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="border-2 border-blue-900 bg-blue-800 p-6 text-center text-white">
